works.description:
Picstitch is a complete rip off of our
app  
InstaFrame. The developer decompiled our app's .apk, stole all the code
and  
assets, changed a few details like the top banner, and then released it as
 
his own. Please run our app (com.coolphotoframes.instaframe) and PicStitch
 
side-by-side. The similarities are startling because it's a stolen
product.
